    "body": "I received the following error when attempting to create a mirror for a rhel7 os on a machine that was running rhel6:\r\n```\r\nspack mirror create -d `pwd` -D -o tmux@2.4 os=rhel7 %gcc@4.8.5\r\n==> Error: No compilers with spec gcc@4.8.5 found for operating system rhel6 and target x86_64\r\n```\r\nI worked around the problem by creating a fake compiler entry for gcc@4.8.5 for rhel6 in the compilers.yaml file.",
